title: How is the Culture of Your Life?
itunes:title: How is the Culture of Your Life?
description:
Culture is in everything we do, our businesses, our families, and our relationships but how seriously do you take the culture in your life? In this episode, we will talk about how important it is to build a culture of growth in your life and how the culture that you set will affect everyone around you.
